::Havotron/Dreadwind/Darkwing::
Havotron looks to the council, then his team, or not team, more like 
servants.  "When will we leave?"

Dreadwind looks to Darkwing.  "We must be ready to fight at all time's 
my brother."

"What is the point, we all die sooner or later."

"Then why is Megatron still alive after millions of years dip stick"

Havotron turns with rage in his eyes. Lifting his superpowerful lasrer 
cannon (the same as megatrons fusion cannon) "Never, ever, mention that 
name in my presence, Dreadwind." With that he fired the bot flying back 
into a wall leaving a dent in it.  He slumped to the floor his chest 
smoking and too weak to stand up.

Darkwing thought of helping him up, but was scared of Havotron 
unleashing the same power on him.
